  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0dba \u0dc5\u0d9f \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a \u0db8\u0dad\u0dca\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Those who went to bribe the police officers have drugs worth one crore",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Peliyagoda Police say that during a raid conducted near the State Engineering Corporation on the Negombo road in Peliyagoda, three persons who tried to bribe the police officers with 30 lakhs were arrested along with cocaine, kush and hash worth more than one crore rupees.",
        "Along with the suspects, one kilo of cocaine, twenty-four kilos of hashish, eight kilos of kush, a jeep and a two-wheeler were also taken into custody by the police.",
        "After observing how the police officers were loading some goods into the jeep from a three-wheeler during the trip, the police said that during the further investigations conducted at the place, there were three cardboard boxes and four suitcases inside the three-wheeler.",
        "The police said that the drugs were stored in the bags and cardboard boxes during the further inspection",
        "At that time, a police officer said that the suspects had given a bribe of 30 lakh rupees to the police officers and told them to send them away from the place.",
        "The arrested suspects are between the ages of 33 and 49 and are residents of Nattandiye and Wattala. Peliyagoda police are conducting investigations."
      ],
